{"tid":683194,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我寫了一個聊天軟件來改善香港的空氣質素","createTime":"2018-05-29T13:23:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-31T07:15:42.000Z","uid":188760,"like":18,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c699547aedfab1c3d0bf4434525f4cb39fd48983","tid":683194,"uid":188760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T13:23:36.000Z","msg":"小弟是一個熱血的IT學生，最近寫了一個手機APP，希望可以改善香港的空氣質素。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/29/205244_40189bd53adfafdc0eaee1ea79925e61.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F29%2F205244_40189bd53adfafdc0eaee1ea79925e61.PNG&h=8840fefa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近年關於香港空氣差的新聞不斷:<br />\n多區空氣污染「爆標」維港灰濛濛<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bastillepost.com/macau/article/28394-%E5%A4%9A%E5%8D%80%E7%A9%BA%E6%B0%A3%E6%B1%A1%E6%9F%93%E3%80%8C%E7%88%86%E6%A8%99%E3%80%8D%E7%B6%AD%E6%B8%AF%E7%81%B0%E6%BF%9B%E6%BF%9B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fmacau%2Farticle%2F28394-%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%258D%2580%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E6%25B1%25A1%25E6%259F%2593%25E3%2580%258C%25E7%2588%2586%25E6%25A8%2599%25E3%2580%258D%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%2581%25B0%25E6%25BF%259B%25E6%25BF%259B&d=YPAu4AnCEAaVi65pa0N96cn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=029a2192\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bastillepost.com/macau/article/28394-%E5%A4%9A%E5%8D%80%E7%A9%BA%E6%B0%A3%E6%B1%A1%E6%9F%93%E3%80%8C%E7%88%86%E6%A8%99%E3%80%8D%E7%B6%AD%E6%B8%AF%E7%81%B0%E6%BF%9B%E6%BF%9B</a><br />\n【空氣污染】臭氧濃度創18年新高　環保署歸咎氣象因素<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/150091/%E7%A9%BA%E6%B0%A3%E6%B1%A1%E6%9F%93-%E8%87%AD%E6%B0%A7%E6%BF%83%E5%BA%A6%E5%89%B518%E5%B9%B4%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98-%E7%92%B0%E4%BF%9D%E7%BD%B2%E6%AD%B8%E5%92%8E%E6%B0%A3%E8%B1%A1%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F150091%2F%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E6%25B1%25A1%25E6%259F%2593-%25E8%2587%25AD%25E6%25B0%25A7%25E6%25BF%2583%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E5%2589%25B518%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%25AB%2598-%25E7%2592%25B0%25E4%25BF%259D%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E6%25AD%25B8%25E5%2592%258E%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E8%25B1%25A1%25E5%259B%25A0%25E7%25B4%25A0&d=YPAu4AnCEAaVi65pa0N96cn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=27abd353\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/150091/%E7%A9%BA%E6%B0%A3%E6%B1%A1%E6%9F%93-%E8%87%AD%E6%B0%A7%E6%BF%83%E5%BA%A6%E5%89%B518%E5%B9%B4%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98-%E7%92%B0%E4%BF%9D%E7%BD%B2%E6%AD%B8%E5%92%8E%E6%B0%A3%E8%B1%A1%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0</a><br />\n維港上空灰濛蒙 14區空氣污染爆表<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.thinkhk.com/article/2017-09/16/23169.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thinkhk.com%2Farticle%2F2017-09%2F16%2F23169.html&d=YPAu4AnCEAaVi65pa0N96cn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=79ee38cf\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.thinkhk.com/article/2017-09/16/23169.html</a><br />\n【霧霾襲港】空氣污染等同倒錢落海　香港2016年一年損失21.6億<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/150091/%E7%A9%BA%E6%B0%A3%E6%B1%A1%E6%9F%93-%E8%87%AD%E6%B0%A7%E6%BF%83%E5%BA%A6%E5%89%B518%E5%B9%B4%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98-%E7%92%B0%E4%BF%9D%E7%BD%B2%E6%AD%B8%E5%92%8E%E6%B0%A3%E8%B1%A1%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F150091%2F%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E6%25B1%25A1%25E6%259F%2593-%25E8%2587%25AD%25E6%25B0%25A7%25E6%25BF%2583%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E5%2589%25B518%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%25AB%2598-%25E7%2592%25B0%25E4%25BF%259D%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E6%25AD%25B8%25E5%2592%258E%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E8%25B1%25A1%25E5%259B%25A0%25E7%25B4%25A0&d=YPAu4AnCEAaVi65pa0N96cn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=27abd353\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/150091/%E7%A9%BA%E6%B0%A3%E6%B1%A1%E6%9F%93-%E8%87%AD%E6%B0%A7%E6%BF%83%E5%BA%A6%E5%89%B518%E5%B9%B4%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98-%E7%92%B0%E4%BF%9D%E7%BD%B2%E6%AD%B8%E5%92%8E%E6%B0%A3%E8%B1%A1%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0</a><br />\n<br />\n香港面積2,755.03平方公里但卻只有16個空氣監測站，這使環保處很難作出有效的空氣評估和有效率的改善措施。<br />\n<br />\n渾濁的空氣正影響我們的健康和下一代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以我們開發了Geopost，一個免費的即時通訊和地圖留言軟件。希望大家對附近的空氣評分，然後做大數據分析，希望能夠更有效地評估每個地方的空氣再設計有效率的改善措施。一齊來改善香港空氣質素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就好似咁：<br />\n <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/29/205850_d1b623bdd37dcc995ff0f93beb127d86.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F29%2F205850_d1b623bdd37dcc995ff0f93beb127d86.jpg&h=dc98c841&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/29/205850_bb8d4c7674111db39546a304a7ed41a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F29%2F205850_bb8d4c7674111db39546a304a7ed41a0.jpg&h=6a7b8162&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nZheng, Y., Liu, F., &amp; Hsieh, H. P. (2013, August). U-air: When urban air quality inference meets big data. In Proceedings of the 19th ACM SIGKDD international conference on Knowledge discovery and data mining (pp. 1436-1444). ACM.<br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\nGeopost支持圖片，聲音，文字和表情符號。大家留言或者評分就會係咪地圖留一個marker, 點marker就可以睇到人地留的野。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n功能：<br />\n你可以隨時隨地在地圖上分享您身邊的事，以文字，語音或者圖片。<br />\n&bull;打破地域認識新朋友<br />\n人在香港島也可看到九龍，新界乃至世界各地的信息，然後參與討論。<br />\n&bull;知道在你身邊發生的事<br />\n通過附近的標記，你可以看到周遭其他使用者的留言，語音及圖片。第一時間知道發生在你身邊的事，還有更多消息等著你來發掘。<br />\n&bull;約朋友在地圖上的指定地點聚會<br />\n到底在約在哪裡聚會？把信息標記在地圖上一目了然，再也不擔心迷路了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.geopostproject.ricky.geopost\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.geopostproject.ricky.geopost&d=YPAu4AnCEAaVi65pa0N96cn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=bc8dbfc9\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.geopostproject.ricky.geopost</a><br />\n還有更多功能留待大家發掘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n會繼續完善功能。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果有任何建議，意見，請PM或者在下面留言。或者在Facebook留言:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Geopost-2139771632978173/?modal=admin_todo_tour\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FGeopost-2139771632978173%2F%3Fmodal%3Dadmin_todo_tour&d=YPAu4AnCEAaVi65pa0N96cn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=dbebff10\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Geopost-2139771632978173/?modal=admin_todo_tour</a>"},{"pid":"b2a8eca17bb7355c264241c31fb2cef7fcaca5b6","tid":683194,"uid":78622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T13:36:59.000Z","msg":"Tldr <br />\nBtw pish"},{"pid":"5eef89c8180c98ac63ebffa736d4dbffa6b44bbb","tid":683194,"uid":34189,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T13:47:00.000Z","msg":"改善好似吹大咗，聊天減唔到懸浮粒子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過用黎監察下應該都唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea8bc5215d9a24385adbba0b275281b2c2f65088","tid":683194,"uid":105207,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T13:51:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"551bcc7b1f0b7471c20ae7ed77d0a7b3cdc81911","t